  <brief_title>Extension Study of Pimecrolimus Cream in Pediatric Patients With Atopic Dermatitis</brief_title>
  <official_title>A Clinical Study Continued From the Confirmatory Study to Validate the Efficacy and Safety of Pimecrolimus Cream in Pediatric Atopic Dermatitis Patients</official_title>
  <sponsors>
